LUMI 🤍 My sweet Petaluma peacefully passed away last night in her sleep. She’d been fighting a mystery illness for a long time that we just couldn’t seem to get to the bottom of. It escalated quickly the last two weeks & came too suddenly. She was only 7. Thank you @lexastiles and all of Luma’s vet friends for trying everything to save her. I’m heartbroken, but happy she’s no longer in pain. If you know me, you know my animals are my entire world. And if you know Petal she was the sweetest, sassiest, SCREACHIEST girl. Her iconic meow (more like MEH) that let you know exactly how over your bullshit she was. My petty little pretty girl. Me and your brothers love you so so much.
@webabybears #LittleFallenStar ⭐️ hits @hbomax tomorrow! Had so much fun voicing Ursa Major, but yikes…things aren’t looking too good for her and Dippy.🔮
